item.title: i am going to punch your arms with a stick
item.description: this weekend was pretty fun. I hung out with the fam. yea know the drill. I apparently let my parents car out of the closet. stupid cars. hiding ALL THE TIME. here be pictures. here are other pictures of a different weekend a week ago. fun fun. but also insanity. some interesting things are happening. it is fn. and not quite expected. but really nice. we shall see how they pan out.
